question: Tahun pinten ingkang ngasilaken paningkatan absolut paling ageng ing 'Pendapatan bunga bersih boten kalebet pasar cib' saking tahun sadèrèngipun?
Pinten 'average interest-earning assets' ing salebeting tigang taun ingkang kasebutaken?
Nalika 'cib markets net interest income' paling dhuwur, pinten reganipun 'average cib markets interest-earning assets' nalika menika?
Kados pundi tren saking 'net interest yield on average cib markets interest-earning assets' saking warsa 2015 ngantos 2017?
answer: Trenipun inggih menika sanget fluktuatif. Tingkat tambah kirang langkung 17.3% saking 1.04 ing warsa 2015 dados 1.22 ing warsa 2016, nanging lajeng mandhap sanget kirang langkung 29.5%, dados 0.86 ing warsa 2017.

question: Sebutaken taun-taun ngendi 'cib markets net interest income' luwih gedhe tinimbang $5.000 yuta lan 'net interest yield on average cib markets interest-earning assets' luwih gedhe tinimbang 1,10.
Ing taun 2016, pinten persen saking 'aset nyengsari bunga rata-rata' ingkang dipunwastani 'aset nyengsari bunga pasar CIB rata-rata'?
Menawi 'cib markets net interest income' ing taun 2017 mundhak 20% nalika 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' tetep sami, pira 'net interest income excluding cib markets' ingkang nembe?

Miturut tabel, menapa wonten gegayutan ingkang saged dipunpirsani antawisipun 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' kaliyan 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' ing salebeting tigang taun punika?
answer: Inggih, wonten gegayutan positif ingkang cetha. Minangka 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' tansah minggah saking $44.620 yuta ing taun 2015 dados $51.410 yuta ing taun 2017, 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' ugi nedahaken paningkatan ingkang tetep saking 2,14% dados 2,36% ing wekdal ingkang sami.

question: Metrik menapa kalih ing tabel menika, nalika ingkang sepindhah dipun bagi kaliyan ingkang kapindho, saged ngétang 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets excluding cib markets'?
answer: net interest income excluding cib markets ( a )
average interest-earning assets excluding cib markets

question: Pundi taun kang 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' kalebu outlier awit saka thukulipun saben taun tinimbang wektu liyane?
answer: Taun 2017 kalebu outlier amarga mundhakipun ingkang katingal. Tambahipun saking taun 2016 dhateng 2017 cacahipun $4.118 yuta ($51.410 - $47.292), ingkang langkung kathah tinimbang tambahipun $2.672 yuta ingkang katingal saking taun 2015 ngantos 2016 ($47.292 - $44.620).
